Explanation:
This line creates categories/groups from numeric values.
Breakdown:
df['sepal_length']
→ Takes sepal length column.
pd.cut()
→ Divides continuous numeric values into groups.
bins=3
→ Creates 3 groups.
labels=["Low", "Medium", "High"]
→ Names of groups.
